<p>Google AI Overviews now appear on nearly half of all tracked search queries. When they show up, <a href="https://searchengineland.com/google-ai-overviews-drive-drop-organic-paid-ctr-464212">organic click-through rates drop by 61%</a>. That single stat reshapes everything you thought you knew about SEO.</p>
